---
description: "Agent boundaries"
alwaysApply: true
---
ChatService is DELETED. ChatOrchestrator replaces it. All references to ChatService are dead code.

project_manager.py is frozen — read and call it, never modify it.

Each agent task has an explicit file scope. Only modify files listed in your task contract.

When a change requires modifying a file outside your scope, stop and describe what you need changed and why.

Shared config files (pyproject.toml, settings.json) have a designated owner per phase. If you need a config change, describe it — the owner agent applies it.

Run existing tests after every change. Add new tests for new code. All tests must pass before considering a task complete.